    <title>hexo博客设置打赏功能</title>
    <link href="http://yambug.github.io/2020_12/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E6%89%93%E8%B5%8F%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD.html"/>
    <id>http://yambug.github.io/2020_12/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E6%89%93%E8%B5%8F%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD.html</id>
    <published>2020-12-15T13:18:13.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-12-15T13:21:09.189Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>首先本博客使用了Hexo,yilia主题</p><p>把你保存的图片放到 themes\yilia\source\img 文件夹里</p><p>打开主题配置文件 _config.yml</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 打赏</span><br><span class="line"># 打赏type设定：0-关闭打赏； 1-文章对应的md文件里有reward:true属性，才有打赏； 2-所有文章均有打赏</span><br><span class="line">reward_type: 2</span><br><span class="line"># 打赏wording</span><br><span class="line">reward_wording: &#39;谢谢您请码农喝咖啡&#39;</span><br><span class="line"># 支付宝二维码图片地址，跟你设置头像的方式一样。比如：&#x2F;assets&#x2F;img&#x2F;alipay.jpg</span><br><span class="line">alipay: #&#x2F;img&#x2F;alizanshang.jpg</span><br><span class="line"># 微信二维码图片地址</span><br><span class="line">weixin: &#x2F;img&#x2F;zanshang.jpg</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>编译  hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g  运行 hexo server 测试是否成功</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;首先本博客使用了Hexo,yilia主题&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;把你保存的图片放到 themes\yilia\source\img 文件夹里&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;打开主题配置文件 _config.yml&lt;/p&gt;
